Hey, that was fast! Are you done?<</speech>>
<<speech "You" "''$name:''">>
Um... yea-<</speech>>
<<speech "nobody" "''Bartender:''">>
Come on, dude. I can smell the shit from here. Go back in there and finish the job.<</speech>>
